5cbca84d47c9f231fb76240bd001","tid":492682,"uid":38671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"又9up<br />\n乜野叫只有八達通<br />\n明明香港好多選擇<br />\n係支那只有支那寶"},{"pid":"6b7f1f4d5c9a0e7bb3c2068a07a52092b756d7f2","tid":492682,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"公道講句，支付寶根本屌打八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八達通零加密，執到就用到，無安全性可言<br />\n<br />\n所謂方便只係因為無能力做任何加密<br />\n<br />\n概念上好唔同，深圳一早有深圳八達通，但只係用黎代替小額實體貨幣嘅手段，完全稱唔上網絡流通嘅貨幣<br />\n<br />\n依加所謂payme Tap n go雖然係電子貨幣，但係普及性太低，而且唔成熟，與其話係香港人嘅電子貨幣，不如話係部份香港人嘅電子貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶可以喺中港使用，將來外國如果要引進一種支付方式針對中國同香港，你覺得佢地會揀支付寶定tap n go?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089a966912b162d7ea8dc494c3edc0ebc3d232d6","tid":492682,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"樓上#5846係隻蠢撚過閪嘅柒頭 可以block柒佢唔駛客氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05edbde8d608676b60cc9098f105329c3bb969f2","tid":492682,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"條友應該等緊奶共機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d609e98f2fd47c286f5c2473cd2a5eb1db5861c","tid":492682,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐支付寶幾時可以出實體卡拍機同匿名用錢"},{"pid":"e7e5a925a6597c50b384ea0ea26ed56537350c80","tid":492682,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公道講句，支付寶根本屌打八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">八達通零加密，執到就用到</span>，無安全性可言<br />\n<br />\n所謂方便只係因為無能力做任何加密<br />\n<br />\n概念上好唔同，深圳一早有深圳八達通，但只係用黎代替小額實體貨幣嘅手段，完全稱唔上網絡流通嘅貨幣<br />\n<br />\n依加所謂payme Tap n go雖然係電子貨幣，但係普及性太低，而且唔成熟，與其話係香港人嘅電子貨幣，不如話係部份香港人嘅電子貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶可以喺中港使用，將來外國如果要引進一種支付方式針對中國同香港，你覺得佢地會揀支付寶定tap n go?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人八達通如果唔見左，一報失就會2小時內停左張卡<br />\n邊到無安全性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔見左部手機都有機比人偷資料啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋講左好多次，技術層面上nfc 係安全過qr code 好多<br />\n問題係香港班死老野根本短視到pk <br />\n唔肯放錢咁可以點？"},{"pid":"383640bfc4dab3a3a1758f1288dd6cc9c8d7572c","tid":492682,"uid":59695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛D wade: 八達通都用qr code, 所以qr code係先進</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>喂喂個post開撚到2啦，想潛撚到幾時啊地頭鼠</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n五毛D wade 答到我點解qr code咁多保安漏洞但都重死撐未?(2)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/480879/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/480879/1?ref=android</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n*圍觀五毛*<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8696c838a1858e7e50aced40ae7dbf2d40cd575","tid":492682,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&quot;國內&quot;，港豬有反過乜楓葉國產品嗎？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4d2c83403dcb138bd3b3dcc317f4ebc28a1efc","tid":492682,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"481b764e0978db9fa51e7790f4c5a180b704d01f","tid":492682,"uid":111081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"係呢班人逢國内野都支持姐，點解一定要推廣支付寶唔推廣八達通付款？<br />\n講真如果逼我用apple pay，我都一樣會反"},{"pid":"83dbcc902a35a4f603ceec86241b060b2024bb2e","tid":492682,"uid":36551,"like":5,"dislike":0,